Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory61.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Based on the coordinate information obtained, this should where the ninth original memory data is located.', 4: '1'}
{2: "What's the matter, Lucia?", 3: '8', 4: 'Is it almost over?', 5: '9'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Nothing, Commandant. I was just thinking that the battle was coming to an end.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'I just... start to feel a bit lonely...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'I\'m not going to take back my comment of "not like a real hero story," but it\'s not a bad one either.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "It's a bit weird. We weren't supposed to have so many feelings about our missions.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Perhaps they are too detached from reality.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "It's another ideal that doesn't belong to our time, real and illusory at the same time.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "It's a bit surprising that this comes from you.", 4: '1'}
{2: "It doesn't sound like you.", 3: '22', 4: "There's nothing wrong with that.", 5: '22'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "That's it, Lee. Be prepared to activate the tactical terminal.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "I wonder what kind of person we'll meet this time...", 4: '1'}

{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'The memory prototype this time is called Catherine. A large part of the data about her is missing. The only information we have now is that she had the ability of healing before.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Catherine', 3: "I'm Catherine, the lord of the Rose Garden. Glad to meet all of you. Sorry to keep you waiting.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Good to see you.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'So are you already aware of our mission and purpose?', 4: '1'}
{2: "What's wrong?", 3: '41', 4: 'Catherine?', 5: '41'}
{2: 'Catherine', 3: "I'm sorry. Perhaps I've been living in the darkness for too long. It's a bit uncomfortable stepping into the bright sunlight.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'I remember...', 3: '43', 4: "It's all right.", 5: '43'}
{2: 'Catherine', 3: 'I used to fear the darkness and constriction. But I knew that everything would be just fine.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Catherine', 3: 'Speaking of which, you remind me of a long-lost friend.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Catherine', 3: "Mr. Commandant, if you fight for me, I'll do everything I can to protect you.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Catherine', 3: "Ah, forget about it. It's just the moment I saw you...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Catherine', 3: "I don't know why, but I just wanna say this to you... one more time.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Miss Catherine, we have something to ask you.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Will you join and help us from now on?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "It would be better... if there's no research or experiments...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Catherine', 3: "Of course, my pleasure. As for research and experiments, I'm not made for that. Besides...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Catherine', 3: "Miss Lucia, you'd be a lot more adorable if you stop being so tense.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Catherine', 3: "Doesn't seem like it.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Catherine', 3: "Doesn't matter, we've got time.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Catherine', 3: 'Here are some scarlet petals for you. May your dreams one day be fulfilled.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Thank you, Catherine.', 3: '68', 4: "Let's go.", 5: '68'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Done. Memory: Catherine. Test passed and recycle completed.', 4: '1'}
